680
00:39:45.041 --> 00:39:46.998
Why I took the blame for it?

681
00:39:46.998 --> 00:39:49.717
Well, I'm sure you had a good
enough reason for doing so.

682
00:39:53.882 --> 00:39:56.050
You don't need to be
good at studying

