00:44:11.003 --> 00:44:13.833
<i>[Longing Heart]</i>

725
00:44:13.833 --> 00:44:15.577
<i>Are you really leaving?</i>

726
00:44:15.577 --> 00:44:17.619
<i>Ji Soo said that she may be
