727
00:44:17.619 --> 00:44:19.728
<i>- Study abroad?
- You quit your job at the school?</i>

728
00:44:19.728 --> 00:44:21.650
<i>Oh, I'm kind of in the
mood for it right now</i>

729
00:44:21.650 --> 00:44:22.789
<i>so do you want to do some
